data.description: Location, Location, Location.  You can't miss this opportunity, with a lot of checkmarks,  a spacious driveway, ample cul de sac privacy that allows for additional parking for guests when they come over, an oversized master bedroom with tray ceilings, a bonus area for study, exercise equipment, crib or comfy couch. The kitchen features granite countertops and a walk-in pantry. A backyard is where you would like to have unforgettable moments with friends and family: all the shopping, dining, and entertainment you want nearby, and easy commute access. Good-graded school district.  WELCOME HOME!
